comment: Set of shared metadata fields for {@link Record}

variables.name: RECORDING_METHOD_ACTIVELY_RECORDED
variables.comment:
* For actively recorded data by the user. * *

For e.g. An exercise session actively recorded by the user using a phone or a watch * device.

variables.name: RECORDING_METHOD_AUTOMATICALLY_RECORDED
variables.comment:
* For passively recorded data by the app. * *

For e.g. Steps data recorded by a watch or phone without the user starting a session.

variables.name: RECORDING_METHOD_MANUAL_ENTRY
variables.comment:
* For manually entered data by the user. * *

For e.g. Nutrition or weight data entered by the user.

variables.name: VALID_TYPES
variables.comment:
* Valid set of values for this IntDef. Update this set when add new type or deprecate existing
     * type.
     *
     * @hide

methods.comment: * @return Client record version if set, 0 otherwise

methods.comment:

methods.comment: * @return Record identifier if set, empty string otherwise
